  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Plein Sud offers a continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options each morning.</p>
<p>Dinner is a three course evening meal with choice of menu and waiter service. Guests are also entitled to a Savoyard mountain specialty meal once per week.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>
<p>Children's meals are available on request.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
