  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double North-Facing Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 17m² with north facing village views. Also available for sole occupancy (please call to book)</p>
<p><strong>Double Garden Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 20m² with a south-facing balcony and garden views. Also available for sole occupancy (please call to book)</p>
<p><strong>Double South-Facing Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 20m² with a balcony and south-facing mountain views</p>
<p><strong>Triple Rooms</strong> sleep three people and are around 20m² with a balcony and south-facing views. They rooms are made up as one double bed and one single bed suited to a child under 11 years old. </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds (specify when booking)</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar/mini-fridge</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Room safe</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival</li>
<li>Rooms are cleaned mid week with linen and towels changed. Daily cleaning available on request.</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request, for children under 2 years. All rooms can take a cot.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
